| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-1714 — Recovery Inhibition (dragonforce)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 49a2e9e5-5ad2-5d34-9f50-61844e465c43"
